{"tid":1923853,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"象腿消失！深田恭子驚現香雞腿","createTime":"2020-03-13T10:03:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T13:37:39.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c11f62de2c81d7a6d52232a2c87bfc7206adee6b","tid":1923853,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T10:03:33.000Z","msg":"37歲日本女星深田恭子一向被指擁有一雙又粗又肥的象腿，但這雙象腿最近已消失得無影無蹤。<br />\n新一期雜誌《Friday》於本月上旬，拍到頭戴Cap帽的恭子現身東京麻布十番的商店街，當時她身穿一條緊身褲，一雙修長美腿相當搶眼。不少網友看完圖片都大表驚訝，因為恭子昔日的象腿已變成幼幼的美腿，幼得來似俗稱的香雞腿，網友無不大叫神奇。<br />\n<br />\n恭子多年前身材肥胖時，常被網友嘲笑她的一雙象腿，其後事務所勒令她減肥，減吃高熱量食物，而恭子亦十分積極，利用4個瘦身方法迫自己瘦身，包括1.衝浪瘦身法、 2.不再飲果汁，每天飲暖水激活新陳代謝、3.早餐吃一條熱量低但營養價值高的香蕉、4.每天回家除衫照鏡，自我審查進度。結果瘦身多年終於有今日成果。"},{"pid":"b6ec41d0a5d8a19c43600858c107793796afb981","tid":1923853,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T10:03:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200313/photo/bkn-20200313123053160-0313_00862_001_01p.jpg?20200313132245\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200313%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200313123053160-0313_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20200313132245&h=1dbeac29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200313/photo/bkn-20200313123053160-0313_00862_001_02p.jpg?20200313132245\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200313%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200313123053160-0313_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20200313132245&h=45a00501&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"252ad3b7839593c90656491da1df24dd68db6199","tid":1923853,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:35:37.000Z","msg":"脾與脾之間好濶"},{"pid":"1f9265c664e004378b432b412a38caf098c2680e","tid":1923853,"uid":192732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"252ad3b7839593c90656491da1df24dd68db6199","tid":1923853,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T1